definitions.definition: The language spoken by the native Algonquin people of central Canada , one of a closely related group of languages and dialects of the Algonquian branch of the Algic language family .

main_definition: The language spoken by the native Algonquin people of central Canada , one of a closely related group of languages and dialects of the Algonquian branch of the Algic language family .

definitions.definition: A member of a native Algonquin people of central Canada.

main_definition: A member of a native Algonquin people of central Canada.
